{"@context":"http://iiif.io/api/presentation/3/context.json","id":"https://digbmc.github.io/pta-manifests/phan/phan-04204/manifest.json","type":"Manifest","label":{"none":["PHAN-04204"]},"metadata":[{"label":{"none":["Timestamp"]},"value":{"none":["0:42:04"]}},{"label":{"none":["Film"]},"value":{"none":["Phantom Thread"]}},{"label":{"none":["Creator"]},"value":{"none":["Paul Thomas Anderson"]}},{"label":{"none":["Distance"]},"value":{"none":["medium shot"]}},{"label":{"none":["Angle"]},"value":{"none":["eye-level"]}},{"label":{"none":["Location"]},"value":{"none":["interior"]}},{"label":{"none":["Movement"]},"value":{"none":["mobile, handheld"]}},{"label":{"none":["Composition"]},"value":{"none":["group shot"]}}],"summary":{"none":["A woman applies makeup in a crowded dressing room."]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-04204/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"homepage":[{"id":"PHAN-04204","type":"Text","format":"text/html","label":{"none":["Object homepage"]}}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-04204/canvas/1","type":"Canvas","height":1080,"width":1920,"label":{"none":["PHAN-04204"]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-04204/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-04204/canvas/1/annopage-1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-04204/canvas/1/annopage-1/anno-1","type":"Annotation","motivation":"painting","target":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-04204/canvas/1","body":{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-04204/tiles/full/1920,1080/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":1080,"width":1920,"service":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-04204/tiles","type":"ImageService3","profile":"http://iiif.io/api/image/3/level0.json"}]}}]}],"annotations":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-04204/canvas/1/page/p1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-04204/canvas/1/5fef08b8-3081-4f28-9ca9-29025cd2861a","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-30T19:12:29.063Z","creator":"g","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>In an interview with Adam Nayman, costume designer Mark Bridges says the following about Reynolds’s clothes: “My colors were probably a bit bolder and a little more photogenic, but something I had to wrap my head around was that the Reynolds Woodcock look was a bit on the way out” (Nayman, <em>Masterworks</em>, 266). That is, indeed, a central tension in the film—Reynolds grows frustrated with demands for “chic” fashion as he attempts to stay true to his vision. On some level, this dynamic may be read as metacommentary from PTA, an acknowledgment of any artist’s desire to maintain control over their art even as market demands shift.&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-04204/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:1213.243606998654,76.79676985195161,562.0457604306864,518.1157469717363"}}},{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-04204/canvas/1/346378dd-005e-40f0-b1af-f535b7c838b8","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-30T19:12:44.782Z","creator":"g","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>Applying her lip color using a handheld mirror, Alma here engages in an aspect of self-fashioning, albeit one within the strictures of Reynolds’s creative act.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-04204/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:521.9919246298789,239.59623149394355,485.814266487214,396.6621803499327"}}}]}]}]}